The dataset includes:

agents_data.csv: synthetic agent profiles and behavioral states.
graph_edges.csv: environment connectivity, hazard, density, and distance values.
graph_nodes.csv: spatial layout of graph nodes.
hazard_snapshot.csv: hazard distribution snapshot.
simulation_metadata.csv: simulation configuration.

The dataset is also available on Zenodo:

https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.19882952
